  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "de75c6e9-6607-4518-8d79-a07fc4662b7f"],
 " appears on the right-hand side of the Lindblad equation for the density \
operator ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  StyleBox["\[Rho]", "TR"]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "bdf51ef7-c09a-4009-8357-e231a6dfd6e1"],
 "."
}], "Notes",
 CellID->632363205,ExpressionUUID->"aef867ef-feaf-4a50-8992-6f01e14d2317"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Physically, the effective Hamiltonian ",
